T02TD1665E:133b-1: shra'i badzra he ru ka gu hya' rtha bya'u ha n'a ma /
T02TD1665E:133b-3: dpal he ru ka'i gsang ba'i don rnam par bkod pa zhes bya ba //
T02TD1665E:133b-4: dpal rdo rje sems dpa' la phyag 'tshal lo //
T02TD1665E:133b-5: thams cad 'byung gnas gsal byed cing //
T02TD1665E:133b-6: gnyis med ma 'dres mdzad mthar phyir //
T02TD1665E:133b-7: stong nyid ye shes drug gi bdag //
T02TD1665E:133b-8: thugs mchog khro bdag phyag 'tshal te //
T02TD1665E:133b-9: dregs byed zhe sdang la sogs skyes //
T02TD1665E:133b-10: nyon mongs lam zhen ru tra sogs //
T02TD1665E:133b-11: 'joms mdzad dpal ldan he ru ka'i //
T02TD1665E:133b-12: gsang don rnam bkod par bya //
T02TD1665E:133b-13: rang bzhin ngag tshul bzang las byung //
T02TD1665E:133b-14: gnyis med yon tan skye bas thob //
T02TD1665E:133b-15: skyabs 'gro byang sems sdom pa can //
T02TD1665E:133b-16: dbang thob dam tshig 'jigs med pa //
T02TD1665E:133b-17: theg chen gsang sngags blo gros mchog //
T02TD1665E:133b-18: he ru ka dpal la dga' bas //
T02TD1665E:133b-19: phyi nang g-yeng ba rab gsal te //
T02TD1665E:133b-21: dur khrod dang ni lha rten dang //
T02TD1665E:133b-22: ma mo'i gnas la sogs 'dug nas //
T02TD1665E:133b-23: rdo rje 'dzin pa'i dgongs pa dag //
T02TD1665E:133b-25: 'gro la snying rje chen po yis //
T02TD1665E:133b-26: bdag gzhan sgrol bar dam bcas nas //
T02TD1665E:133b-27: sbyor ldan nus mthu gsum bskyed pas //
T02TD1665E:133b-28: bdag dang 'gro ba spyang ba dang //
T02TD1665E:133b-29: dbang po'i dkyil 'khor mdun dmigs te //
T02TD1665E:133b-30: dang po bya ba'i rim rdzogs spyang //
T02TD1665E:133b-31: sgrib sogs las grol dag byed pa'i //
T02TD1665E:133b-32: sems can tshad med blo yis gzung //
T02TD1665E:133b-33: bar chad bgegs bsal srung byed pa'i //
T02TD1665E:133b-35: phyogs bcu khro bo'i tshogs bskyed pa'i //
T02TD1665E:133b-36: cho ga rang gi las bzhin bsgom //
T02TD1665E:133b-37: thams cad spros bral de bzhin nyid //
T02TD1665E:134a-2: 'gro la phan pa'i thugs rje'i rgyun //
T02TD1665E:134a-3: stong gsal nam mkha'i shugs ltar byung //
T02TD1665E:134a-4: rdo rje sems dpang skal bzang dpal //
T02TD1665E:134a-6: ae yam bam lam mam sum ram //
T02TD1665E:134a-7: aom na ma: srba ta th'a ga ta aa nu r'a ga ya mi mntal la ha'um bhr'aum /
T02TD1665E:134a-8: chos 'byung nam mkha'i rang bzhin las //
T02TD1665E:134a-9: byung ba'i dkyil 'khor rim bzhin brtsigs //
T02TD1665E:134a-10: ri rab me 'od rgyan gsal zhing //
T02TD1665E:134a-11: kha dog dbyibs rgyan mtshan mar bcas //
T02TD1665E:134a-12: bde gshegs yon tan snang ba'i gnas //
T02TD1665E:134a-13: sna tshogs padma rin po che //
T02TD1665E:134a-14: 'khor lo sna tshogs rdo rje'i dbus //
T02TD1665E:134a-15: khang pa rdo rje sgo khyud dang //
T02TD1665E:134a-16: rta babs bzhi yis mdzes byas pa //
T02TD1665E:134a-17: sa gzhi nam mkha' logs kyi phyogs //
T02TD1665E:134a-18: rigs kyi rin chen 'tsher ba la //
T02TD1665E:134a-19: rang byung nyi shu rtsa lnga'i 'od //
T02TD1665E:134a-21: sna lnga'i rtsig pa dra ba dang //
T02TD1665E:134a-22: dra phyed rin chen pha gus mtshan //
T02TD1665E:134a-23: rdo rje mtshan pa'i ka ba rgyang //
T02TD1665E:134a-24: rin chen mu tig me tog phreng //
T02TD1665E:134a-25: rgyal mtshan bla rnga yab gdugs //
T02TD1665E:134a-26: 'dod yon lnga yi lha mo 'khyug / zla phed rdo rje rin chen //
T02TD1665E:134a-27: ba dan dril bu sgra snyan sgrogs //
T02TD1665E:134a-28: pho phrang zla gam sgo can la /
T02TD1665E:134a-29: re'u mig dgu pa thod pas mtshan //
T02TD1665E:134a-30: sna tshogs padma'i gdan mdzes shing //
T02TD1665E:134a-31: rdo rje phreng bas rnam par mtshan //
T02TD1665E:134a-32: mtshams su bum pa gang ba bzhi //
T02TD1665E:134a-33: rigs kyi mtshan mas rnam par mdzes //
T02TD1665E:134a-34: khyams bzhi cha yi mtshams bzhi dang /
T02TD1665E:134a-35: sgo gnas la sogs padma'i gdan //
T02TD1665E:134a-36: phyi rol ra ba'i rim gsum rgyab //
T02TD1665E:134a-37: phyogs mtshams dur khrod chen po brgyad //
T02TD1665E:134a-38: de mtha' 'dod pa'i longs spyod dang //
T02TD1665E:134a-39: rdo rje ra bas bskor ba yi //
T02TD1665E:134a-40: thams cad na mkha'i mtshan nyid de //
T02TD1665E:134a-41: nam mkha' la yang mtshan nyid med //
T02TD1665E:134a-42: khams gsum dag ni ma lus pa //
T02TD1665E:134a-43: thams cad sgyu ma lta bu ste //
T02TD1665E:134a-44: ji ltar sgyu ma thams cad du //
T02TD1665E:134a-45: mthong sgyu ma thams cad du //
T02TD1665E:134a-46: mthong ba dag ni reg par 'gyur //
T02TD1665E:134a-47: dmigs su yid pa ma yin te //
T02TD1665E:134a-48: de bzhin 'gro ba kun gyi tshul //
T02TD1665E:134a-49: rnam thar sgo bzhi snyoms 'jug go //
T02TD1665E:134a-51: phyogs bcu'i rgyal bas bskul mdzad de //
T02TD1665E:134a-52: mngon byang lha yis rdzogs skur gyur //
T02TD1665E:134a-53: sems dang sems dpa'i ting 'dzin dang //
T02TD1665E:134a-54: byang chub spyod pa sna tshogs nyid //
T02TD1665E:134b-0: de bzhin bdud dang bdud las @134b rgyal //
T02TD1665E:134b-1: de ni byang chub sangs rgyas yin //
T02TD1665E:134b-2: aom ma h'a su kha badzra sa tva a'a: ha'um bam ho: su ra ta stvam /
T02TD1665E:134b-3: rdo rje sems dpa' bde chen sku //
T02TD1665E:134b-4: dkar zhing dmar ba'i mdong gsal 'od //
T02TD1665E:134b-5: zhal bzhi rnams gzigs phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1665E:134b-6: dang po rdo rje rtse lnga 'bar //
T02TD1665E:134b-7: rdo rje kha tva'm dril bcas 'khrol //
T02TD1665E:134b-8: 'og ma gnyis kyis mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1665E:134b-9: mtshan dpe phyag rgya lnga yis brgyanh //
T02TD1665E:134b-10: stod g-yogs dar ser dang ris can //
T02TD1665E:134b-11: sku smad tshe gu'i na bza' la //
T02TD1665E:134b-12: rin chen phreng ba'i rked chings 'dri la //
T02TD1665E:134b-13: mgul chu do shal dpung rgyan dang //
T02TD1665E:134b-14: phyag zhabs gdu bu se mo do //
T02TD1665E:134b-15: rdo rje rtse lnga'i phyag rgya ni //
T02TD1665E:134b-16: gnas lnga dag tu gtug bya ste //
T02TD1665E:134b-17: sngags kyi bde gshegs thams cad kyi //
T02TD1665E:134b-18: sku gsung thugs sogs rnam par bsam //
T02TD1665E:134b-19: aom na ma: srba ta tha' ga ta ka' ya ba'g tsitta guna karmrma /
T02TD1665E:134b-20: badzra sva a'a bha' a'a tma ko~ham //
T02TD1665E:134b-21: lus kyi sbu'i gnas rnams su //
T02TD1665E:134b-22: dkyi 'khor drug gi rdul phran gnas //
T02TD1665E:134b-23: mkha' dbyings dbang phyug rgya yis //
T02TD1665E:134b-24: gnas kun byin gyis brlab par bya //
T02TD1665E:134b-25: aom dha rma' dha' tu badzra sva bha' wa a'a tma ko& ham /
T02TD1665E:134b-26: lag pa shin tu brkyang ba yis //
T02TD1665E:134b-27: mdzub mi gnyis ni mdud par bcings //
T02TD1665E:134b-28: gung me mthe bo'i rtse mi can //
T02TD1665E:134b-29: rdo rje phyag rgya yang bsgyur bteg //
T02TD1665E:134b-30: bskor zhing kun du bskor nas kyang// khro gnyer du ni legs gzhag bya ;
T02TD1665E:134b-32: rtna ma' le aa bhi shinytsa tram //
T02TD1665E:134b-33: pa ta lam aa bhi shinytsa aom /
T02TD1665E:134b-35: byin brlabs rigs kyi dbu rgyan gyis //
T02TD1665E:134b-36: rgyu yi mgon po rdo rje 'chang //
T02TD1665E:134b-37: dpal ldan he ru ka yi sku //
T02TD1665E:134b-38: cha lugs mtshan ma rgyan gsal gyur //
T02TD1665E:134b-41: zhal g-yas zhi ba'i rang bzhin dkar //
T02TD1665E:134b-42: dbus ma mthing nag drag po'izhal //
T02TD1665E:134b-43: g-yon pa rmongs byed ser po ste //
T02TD1665E:134b-44: rgyab ma chags mdzad dmar ba'o //
T02TD1665E:134b-45: smin mtshams khro gnyer glog bzhin gyur //
T02TD1665E:134b-46: spyan dmar ma che gtsigs 'jigs pa'i zhal //
T02TD1665E:134b-47: dbu skra smar ser gag las //
T02TD1665E:134b-48: spun rnams rdo rje gyen du 'khyil //
T02TD1665E:134b-49: sgeg pa dpa' ba 'jigs su rung //
T02TD1665E:134b-50: dgod dang gshed dang 'jigs par byed //
T02TD1665E:134b-51: snying rje rngam dang zhi ba yis //
T02TD1665E:134b-52: sku gsung thugs kyi gar thabs can //
T02TD1665E:134b-53: g-yas g-yon dang po rdo rje dang //
T02TD1665E:134b-54: rdo rje kha ta'm dril bur bcas //
T02TD1665E:135a-2: pags pa rlung gi tshul du bskor //
T02TD1665E:135a-3: gsum pa gnyis na mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1665E:135a-4: g-yas kyi bzhi pas dung khrag 'dizn //
T02TD1665E:135a-5: ga-uon gyi bzhi pa thod pa ru //
T02TD1665E:135a-6: snying chen po yis bkangs pa'o //
T02TD1665E:135a-7: la lar zhal gcig phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1665E:135a-8: g-yas gnyis rdo rje dung khrag 'dzin ;
T02TD1665E:135a-9: / g-yon gnyis thod pa zhags par bcas //
T02TD1665E:135a-10: rdo rje kha ta'm se ral kha //
T02TD1665E:135a-11: la lar rdo rje bha ndha dmar //
T02TD1665E:135a-12: kha ta'm ga la rgya brten mdzad// glang chen stag gi pags pa yis //
T02TD1665E:135a-13: stod smad sku yin bzar mnabs //
T02TD1665E:135a-14: dlu rgyal thod pa'i phreng ba yis //
T02TD1665E:135a-15: sku yi gnas brgyad rnam spras shing //
T02TD1665E:135a-16: lha chen dpa' bo'i g-yang gzhi dag //
T02TD1665E:135a-17: mtshan ma chen po na bzer gsol //
T02TD1665E:135a-18: sku la thal bas byugs pa la //
T02TD1665E:135a-19: khrag dang zhag gi mos mtshan //
T02TD1665E:135a-20: phyag rgya lnga yis mtshan pa la //
T02TD1665E:135a-21: snyan gang nyi zla rin chen phreng //
T02TD1665E:135a-22: thun mong rgyan sogs tshangs pa la //
T02TD1665E:135a-23: khyad par rtags kyis rnam spras pa'o //
T02TD1665E:135a-24: rang byung ngo bo las byung ba'o //
T02TD1665E:135a-25: kro dhi shva ris 'jo sgreg stabs //
T02TD1665E:135a-26: sku mdog sngo skya nam mkha'i lus //
T02TD1665E:135a-27: se ral kha yi tshul dag tu //
T02TD1665E:135a-28: kha tva'm la rgyab rten bcas /
T02TD1665E:135a-30: // lag pa g-yon pas thod pa thogs //
T02TD1665E:135a-31: g-yas pas ba dan gsum pa'i phyag //
T02TD1665E:135a-32: rin chen 'bar ba'i rgyan gyis mtshan //
T02TD1665E:135a-33: phyung nas byin gyis brlabs mdzad de //
T02TD1665E:135a-34: thabs dang shes rab ldan par 'gyur //
T02TD1665E:135a-35: gnas gzhi yi ge mtshan ma sngags //
T02TD1665E:135a-36: dkyil 'khor gdan la legs gnas rnams //
T02TD1665E:135a-37: spro dang bsdu ba'i rim pa yis //
T02TD1665E:135a-38: phyag rgya bzhi yi rnam par gsal// lha mo'i bum pas khrus byas te //
T02TD1665E:135a-39: dbang bskur rigs kyi bdag por bsam //
T02TD1665E:135a-40: gri: las skyes pa'i ling ga ni //
T02TD1665E:135a-41: rdo rje gsang lam phat kyis mtshan //
T02TD1665E:135a-42: aa yig dag byas bha ga'i dbyibs //
T02TD1665E:135a-44: sna tshogs brda yis bskul byas nas //
T02TD1665E:135a-45: thabs shes gnyis med rol par mdzad //
T02TD1665E:135a-46: aom pra be sha ya phat //
T02TD1665E:135a-47: aa la la la la ho//
T02TD1665E:135a-48: byang chub sems kyi 'od zer gyis //
T02TD1665E:135a-49: phyogs bcu'i dkyil 'khor mnyes par mdzad //
T02TD1665E:135a-50: lha rnams rang la gzhug bya ste //
T02TD1665E:135a-51: gnyis ka'i dga' ba rab spel //
T02TD1665E:135a-52: khams gsum 'gro gnas dag pa dang //
T02TD1665E:135a-53: rnal 'byor mtshan ma rnam par spyang //
T02TD1665E:135b-0: gsang ba'i gnas su gzhal yas khang @135b rgyan sogs gdan rnams sngon bzhin 'byung //
T02TD1665E:135b-1: thig les gnas su mtshan byas nas //
T02TD1665E:135b-2: spros pas yi ge'o dkyil 'khor gsal //
T02TD1665E:135b-3: hrai: las rdo rje he ru ka //
T02TD1665E:135b-4: gsang gnas dbus kyi padma pa'o //
T02TD1665E:135b-5: hrai: las shar du goo ra'i ma //
T02TD1665E:135b-6: hni las tsoo ra'i lha yi phyogs //
T02TD1665E:135b-7: nub tu dziha las pra mo ste //
T02TD1665E:135b-8: dzi las be ta' gyang du'o// mtshams bzhir ha'um phat bon las //
T02TD1665E:135b-10: ya wa ral bzhi po las //
T02TD1665E:135b-11: mda' gnon 'dzin ma la sogs rnams //
T02TD1665E:135b-12: me tshams sogs kyi gru chad la //
T02TD1665E:135b-13: rim pa bzhin du gnas pa yin //
T02TD1665E:135b-14: aa a'a me tog spos me ma //
T02TD1665E:135b-15: aam aa: mar me dri chab ste //
T02TD1665E:135b-16: bar 'khyams mtshams kyi gnas bzhi ru //
T02TD1665E:135b-17: lha mo bzhi ru gnas pa yin //
T02TD1665E:135b-18: dza: las rta srin 'phang mtho ma //
T02TD1665E:135b-19: ha'um las phag gdong mche ba can //
T02TD1665E:135b-20: bam las nyi zla me 'bar ma //
T02TD1665E:135b-21: ho: las thal byed sgo bzhir gnas //
T02TD1665E:135b-22: aom shra'i he ru ka badzra sa ma yi hi //
T02TD1665E:135b-23: srba shta nas ma ya mu tra //
T02TD1665E:135b-25: phyogs bcu'i 'gro ba spyang mdzad nas //
T02TD1665E:135b-26: yab yum sku la gzhug par bya /
T02TD1665E:135b-27: ha'um badzra gu he ddhe ba ra ma ha' yo gi shva ri di //
T02TD1665E:135b-28: goo ra'i dmar ser zhi ba mo //
T02TD1665E:135b-29: zhal bzhi g-yon brkyang gar gyis bzhugs //
T02TD1665E:135b-30: phyag brgyad g-yas kyi mda' bzhi la //
T02TD1665E:135b-31: tshangs la chden po'i mgo bzhi dbyangs //
T02TD1665E:135b-32: ha'um ha'um badzra tsnta shvai ra kha tva'i ga ma ha' badzra ka pa' la ma' la mghu te ru du //
T02TD1665E:135b-33: tsoo ra'i dmar ser drag pa mo //
T02TD1665E:135b-34: g-yon na lcags kyug g-yas pa yi //
T02TD1665E:135b-35: gung mos 'khor lo rtse brgyad bstod //
T02TD1665E:135b-36: kha tva'm brten zhabs g-yas bteg //
T02TD1665E:135b-37: aom badzra ma ra yo gi dza: //
T02TD1665E:135b-38: phra mo dmar gnag phyag pa bzhi ma //
T02TD1665E:135b-39: dang pos rdo rje kham phor 'chang //
T02TD1665E:135b-41: g-yas brkyang rmongs tshul gong ma phag //
T02TD1665E:135b-42: aom badzra pre ta ke dzi //
T02TD1665E:135b-43: be ta dkar mo slong mdzad tshul //
T02TD1665E:135b-44: dga' ba'i gar thabs ga yas pa na //
T02TD1665E:135b-45: thod pa mtshan ldan bdud rtsis gang //
T02TD1665E:135b-46: g-yon pa ba dan gsum pa'i phyag //
T02TD1665E:135b-47: aom badzra pra ha ri ni tram //
T02TD1665E:135b-48: pu kka drag mo sna tshogs mdog //
T02TD1665E:135b-49: g-yas pas rdo rje rtse lngag gsor //
T02TD1665E:135b-50: g-yon pas dpag bsam lcug ma 'dzin //
T02TD1665E:135b-51: gar gyis gzigs thabs 'gyur ba bzhin //
T02TD1665E:135b-52: ha'um badzra sha'u la aa ki bi da phat /
T02TD1665E:135b-54: g-yas na ra skyes rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1665E:136a-2: gzhan gyi srog 'phrog las la brtson //
T02TD1665E:136a-3: h'um badzra kro dha tstshinda ka mat /
T02TD1665E:136a-4: gha sma ser gang ro ldegs tshul //
T02TD1665E:136a-5: g-yas pas ral gri g-yon me thab //
T02TD1665E:136a-6: g-yon brkyang gar gyis 'gyur bag can //
T02TD1665E:136a-7: myur ba'i phrin las grub par mdzod //
T02TD1665E:136a-8: aom badzra sa ma ya p'a she phat //
T02TD1665E:136a-9: sme sha mthing nag phyag bzhi pa //
T02TD1665E:136a-10: phyag gnyis rdo rje dung khrag 'dzin //
T02TD1665E:136a-11: g-yon gnyis thod pa zhags par bcas //
T02TD1665E:136a-12: rdo rje kha tv'am ser la kha //
T02TD1665E:136a-13: kun kyang thod phreng sbrul gdug dang //
T02TD1665E:136a-14: zhing lpags rlon pa rin chen phreng //
T02TD1665E:136a-15: gdan ni sna tshogs padma la //
T02TD1665E:136a-16: zhing dang nyi mas mtshan pa'o //
T02TD1665E:136a-18: mda' 'dzin dkar mo mda' dang gzhu //
T02TD1665E:136a-19: me mtshams phyogs kyi padma la //
T02TD1665E:136a-20: bam ma ha r'a ti badzra ho //
T02TD1665E:136a-21: kha tv'am ser mo kha tv'am ga //
T02TD1665E:136a-22: rdo rje dril 'phan bden bral mtshams //
T02TD1665E:136a-23: aom badzra lo tsa me yam ya /
T02TD1665E:136a-25: rtsibs brgyad 'dzin ma rlung gi phyogs //
T02TD1665E:136a-26: ra ma h'a shr'i badzra ra tra hri /
T02TD1665E:136a-27: sna tshogs ba dan ljang gu la //
T02TD1665E:136a-28: sna tshogs ba dan dbang ldan mtshams //
T02TD1665E:136a-30: me tog ljang ser rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1665E:136a-31: gzhong thogs me yi mtshams su gnas //
T02TD1665E:136a-33: spos ma dkar ser rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1665E:136a-34: pog phor bden bral phyogs su gnas//
T02TD1665E:136a-36: mar me dmar mo rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1665E:136a-37: gsal 'dzin rlung gi mtshams su gnas //
T02TD1665E:136a-39: dri chab ljangs gu rdo rjes mtshan //
T02TD1665E:136a-40: dag 'thor dbang ldan mtshams su gnas //
T02TD1665E:136a-41: aom badzra aam ku sha dza:/
T02TD1665E:136a-42: rta gdong dkar mo lcags kyu dang //
T02TD1665E:136a-43: thod pa rta mgo ljang gu shar //
T02TD1665E:136a-44: aom badzra pra be sha h'um //
T02TD1665E:136a-45: phag gdong sngon mo g-yas mche ba //
T02TD1665E:136a-46: g-yon zhags lho yi sgo la gnas //
T02TD1665E:136a-47: aom badzra shri kha le bam /
T02TD1665E:136a-48: snang ba dmar mo phyogs gnyis kyis //
T02TD1665E:136a-49: nyi zla lcags sgrog nub kyi phyogs //
